This component just includes the end steps when you aren't adding pages or complex content and don't need to test accessibility.

It makes the doc md file easier to read and edit.

Compare to the standard-end-steps component.

Review your changes.

Commit all your changes to GitHub.

Request approval of your changes from the original requestor.

Merge with the main branch.
